                     <interp inst="t17890225-25-off120" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890225-25-off120" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17890225-25-cd121" type="crimeDate">20th day of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890225-25-off120 t17890225-25-cd121"></join>, 478 lb. weight of lead, value 40 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17890225-25-victim332" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Dyer
